verbose_text: The results suggested that the luciferase signal of the Wt-let-7d / ATG16L1 cotransfection group was significantly decreased in cells treated with the let-7d mimic compared with in cells treated with the NC mimic (P < 0.05), while there was no significant difference in the luciferase activity of the Mut-let-7d / ATG16L1 3'UTR (P> 0.05).
